description:
How can we stay healthy during #coronavirus? Get plenty of sunlight, rest, and sleep. Avoid all things harmful and use all those things, in moderation, that are #healthy. 

Here are tips from Dr. Peter Landless, Director of Health Ministries for the Seventh-day Adventist Church. Learn more from #HealthMinistries here: https://healthministries.com/
